HEADWORD: Bickern
<hw>Bick"ern</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>bigorne</ets>. See <er>Bicorn</er>.]</ety> <def>An anvil ending in
